story :
A hunter who managed to save a young deer but was injured after being clawed by a tiger on his shoulder torn his bones. Accidentally that day the sun contained more UV rays than usual and entered the hunter's wound and made the wound heal instantly. In addition to healing, hunters have new powers by solar power.
